    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Every responsible firearm owner knows the importance of keeping your weapons clean. With the ASR Outdoor 18 Piece Gun Cleaning Brush Set, you can ensure that your firearms are clean, polished, rust-free and dependable.<BR><BR>First included in this set are 10 brushes, all featuring nylon bristles. Nylon is a safe and effective material for making short work of cleaning firearms. The brushes can be used with paste, acid, glue and other cleaning solutions, making them a great addition to any gun cleaning kit.<BR><BR>All of the brushes are double-ended, with one large brush head (1.5\" length) and one small brush head (1\" length) so you can clean even the hard to reach places. The large brush head has 3 rows of bristles, while the small brush head has just one row that can fit into small areas</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n<html>\n<head>\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%)