\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">855569007638</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">NYLON BRISTLES - Nylon is a Safe and Effective Material for Cleaning Firearms and Other Machined Parts</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DOUBLE-ENDED TOOLS - Each Brush Comes with One Large Brush Head (1.5\") and One Small Brush Head (1\") for Cleaning Large or Hard to Reach Pieces</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">CLEAN AND POLISH - Removes Rust, Paint, Residue and More from Your Firearm | Regular Cleaning Helps Ensure Weapon is Functioning Properly for Reliable Use</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Handles Made of High-quality Plastic Suitable for Use with Acids, Glues, Pastes and More | Great Tools for Crafting, Hobbies and Automotive</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPACT DESIGN - Overall Length of Brushes is 7\" | Brushes Easily Fit in Most Gun Cleaning Kits, Pouches or Carrying Cases</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Double Sided Gun Cleaning Brushes and Pick Tools 18 Piece Set</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">29.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Every responsible firearm owner knows the importance of keeping your weapons clean. With the ASR Outdoor 18 Piece Gun Cleaning Brush Set, you can ensure that your firearms are clean, polished, rust-free and dependable.\n\nFirst included in this set are 10 brushes, all featuring nylon bristles. Nylon is a safe and effective material for making short work of cleaning firearms. The brushes can be used with paste, acid, glue and other cleaning solutions, making them a great addition to any gun cleaning kit.\n\nAll of the brushes are double-ended, with one large brush head (1.5\" length) and one small brush head (1\" length) so you can clean even the hard to reach places. The large brush head has 3 rows of bristles, while the small brush head has just one row that can fit into small areas. The overall length of the brushes is about 7\" which will fit in most cleaning kits, pouches or carrying cases, ensuring that you'll have the brushes on hand whenever you need them. \n\nAdditionally, we've included an assortment of cleaning tools: 3 double-sided brushes and 2 double-sided picks. One side is large for surface scrubbing, and the other is small for cleaning hard to reach areas. Brushes are made out of brass, copper, and nylon to get all the dirt and grime out of the way. \n\nLastly, we've added in 3 more brushes, all featuring different types of bristles for a variety of cleaning options - plastic, nylon, and copper. This range of bristle options is great for cleaning materials that may need a softer or more abrasive scrubbing. The brushes can be used with paste, acid, glue and other cleaning solutions, making them a great addition to any gun cleaning kit.\n\nIn addition to cleaning, polishing, removing rust or removing paint from your firearms, these brushes are also great for hobbies, crafting and automotive hardware purposes. Make sure to keep a set of these brushes on hand before your next hunting trip, range session or hobby project!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\